# The following rule ensures that all files in this repository use LF line endings regardless of the operating system.
# This is important for consistency and to avoid issues with line endings when running scripts or tests in different environments.
#
# see https://docs.github.com/en/get-started/getting-started-with-git/configuring-git-to-handle-line-endings
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf